data.description: Unique opportunities abound for this cute, centrally located townhome.  Do you want to own a home and produce supplemental rental income at the same time? Do you want to invest in 2 easy rental properties?  Take a  look at Locust Street West in Hampton, SC.  This two story 2 unit townhome is perfect.  New roof (2019) and new water heater (2021). One half of the building, Unit 113, is being updated with new carpet and paint throughout.  New flooring in Unit 113 also to be completed in the downstair half bath AND upstairs full bath. Excellent potential larger investment opportunity available as two adjacent buildings are also for sale. The home is centrally located; easy distance to playground, library, bank and post office. Sold as is.
